    <summary>DDD Value Objects: immutable, identity-free domain types defined entirely by their attributes. Self-validate in constructor, implement domain operations, replace primitives.</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>ddd</tag>
      <tag>value-objects</tag>
      <tag>immutability</tag>
      <tag>domain-model</tag>
      <tag>primitive-obsession</tag>
    </tags>
